---
import Container from '../components/Container.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-surface/30">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About me</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Data Engineer with a Master's degree in Data Processing and Software Engineering background. I specialize in cloud architectures, high-performance data pipelines, and distributed big data solutions.
        </p>

        <p>
          My passion is designing scalable systems that process millions of events per second, from medallion architectures on Azure Databricks to real-time streaming on GCP. I've worked on massive data transformations for e-commerce and fintech companies.
        </p>

        <p>
          I'm specialized in technologies like <span class="text-accent-cyan font-medium">Azure Databricks, Delta Lake, Apache Spark, GCP Dataflow, and BigQuery</span>. I build end-to-end solutions that not only process data but generate measurable business value.
        </p>

        <p>
          Available for senior roles, freelance projects, and data architecture collaborations. Always open to technical challenges that require critical thinking and performance optimization.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
